{"id":125005,"type":1,"name":"花のあすか組！外伝","image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/cover/m/ee/7d/125005_Ai1aa.jpg","summary":"「花之飞鸟组」的故事实际上若以「飞鸟传」而言，始于外传中的补述：九乐飞鸟出生于优渥环境的顶点少女，理所当然的品学兼优，然而上了国中后却因此种背景。而被同学/学校形成之微社会结构欺侮排挤，割腕自杀未遂。她的理所当然的象牙塔人生，在此起了转折点……十四岁的她，在所谓“不良”的社会寻得答案，在这个以强者意志为王的世界/系统，她成了飞鸟神话……","info":"<li><span>中文名: </span>花之飞鸟组！ 外传</li><li><span>册数: </span>6</li><li><span>作者: </span><a href=\"/person/9686\">高口里純</a></li><li><span>出版社: </span><a href=\"/person/518\">角川書店</a>、<a href=\"/person/7611\">尖端出版</a></li><li><span>连载杂志: </span><a href=\"/person/8516\">月刊Asuka</a></li>","collection":{"wish":1,"collect":1},"tags":[{"name":"漫画系列","count":1}],"staff":[{"id":9686,"image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/crt/g/55/6b/9686_prsn_2l80N.jpg","name":"高口里纯","desc":"作者"},{"id":7611,"image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/crt/g/6d/b5/7611_prsn_9285i.jpg","name":"台湾尖端","desc":"出版社"},{"id":518,"image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/crt/g/5a/52/518_prsn_ZwMWM.jpg","name":"角川书店","desc":"出版社"},{"id":8516,"image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/crt/g/15/13/8516_prsn_pKJG1.jpg","name":"月刊Asuka","desc":"连载杂志"}],"relations":[{"id":124976,"image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/cover/m/ee/cf/124976_b0jjb.jpg","title":"花のあすか組!","type":"续集","url":"https://bgm.tv/subject/124976"}],"comic":[{"id":125006,"name":"花のあすか組! (外伝1)","image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/cover/c/4d/4f/125006_jp.jpg"},{"id":125007,"name":"花のあすか組! (外伝2)","image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/cover/c/6e/b9/125007_jp.jpg"},{"id":125008,"name":"花のあすか組! (外伝3)","image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/cover/c/e1/de/125008_jp.jpg"},{"id":125009,"name":"花のあすか組! (外伝4)","image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/cover/c/cd/e0/125009_jp.jpg"},{"id":125010,"name":"花のあすか組! (外伝5)","image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/cover/c/5c/79/125010_jp.jpg"},{"id":125011,"name":"花のあすか組! (外伝6)","image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/cover/c/19/e4/125011_jp.jpg"}]}